metadata.name: Salvator Mundi in Afghanistan
metadata.description:
Salvator Mundi is one of the most famous characters and portraits, painted in 1500 by Leonardo Da Vinci.

But where is he now in 2022?

We show you that Salvator Mundi is in Afghanistan.
Mr. Jesus reminds us that we are all responsible for this country.

We don't recognize the Taliban Regime, and the people of Afghanistan are not alone.
